### ── SALES SERVICE (/sales) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev
### Flow: createOrder → (PaymentService capture) → completeOrder

### 1. Create order — Customer Bauer, VW Golf GTI (MUC)
# @name createOrder
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales/createOrder
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000010",
  "deliveryType": "HOME_DELIVERY"
}

### 2. List orders — Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales/Orders
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 3. List orders — Customer Bauer (own orders only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales/Orders
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 4. Cancel order — Customer Bauer
### orderId: replace with ID returned from step 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales/cancelOrder
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "REPLACE_WITH_ID"
}

### 5. Complete order — Manager (manual completion after payment)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales/completeOrder
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "REPLACE_WITH_ID"
}

### 6. Try to cancel another customer's order — should be rejected
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales/cancelOrder
Authorization: {{customerHoffmannAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "REPLACE_WITH_ID"
}
